                ["title"] = "更新修复说明",
                ["body"] = "<div data-lark-html-role=\"root\">\n<div data-page-id=\"CzqNduNd2o6Cf8xzGYHcoo41nZd\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnETgr4laOw11vykzkzpnhfd\">\n<div data-page-id=\"K09edkqYBoANXexLmkTcGy91nEh\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcn8oRF73SPv8iKzk3DOWIBQf\"><img src=\"http://pan01-cdn-dna-ali.shyxhy.com/upload/99-更新修复说明.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"728\" height=\"200\"></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcn8oRF73SPv8iKzk3DOWIBQf\">亲爱的狩月人：</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnY55ZHJG9HeSuFG9YRKNgCc\">为了保证更好的游戏体验，《二重螺旋》将持续对游戏内问题进行修复，修复期间给各位狩月人带来的不便，敬请见谅，个别已知的特殊问题正在努力处理中，后续将通过更新的方式修复，再次感谢大家的支持与理解。</div>\n<h3 class=\"heading-3 ace-line old-record-id-doxcnYhJPhpi315tddrc6ojYgAf\"><span style=\"color: rgb(248, 153, 52);\">▍更新内容说明</span></h3>\n<div data-zone-id=\"0\" data-line-index=\"0\" data-line=\"true\"><span style=\"color: rgb(248, 153, 52);\"><strong>2025年11月15日</strong></span></div>\n<div data-zone-id=\"0\" data-line-index=\"1\" data-line=\"true\">✦ 修复了在沉浸式戏剧中保存阵容时有极小概率的情况下会保存异常，导致无法进入游戏的问题。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnT3syFxBfYNV9mGYsL8MPMs\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div data-page-id=\"H5YfdXBlKoLyEvxlKyZc6cTdnje\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnT3syFxBfYNV9mGYsL8MPMs\"><span style=\"color: rgb(248, 153, 52);\"><strong>2025年11月14日</strong></span></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnT3syFxBfYNV9mGYsL8MPMs\">✦ 修复了在锻造装饰时，取消锻造会直接获得饰品的问题。（本次更新后将扣除重复获取饰品转化为的「水色棱镜」道具）</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnDxGryFToZVSdvVDTpT5IBb\">✦ 修复了【西比尔】通过【指尖风暴】召唤的【召唤物&middot;紊乱雷球】触发的【灭顶风暴】只能对范围内一名目标造成伤害的问题。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-E9WOdte45oh6qexDRGKcx2nIn3y\">✦ 修复了【西比尔】通过【指尖风暴】召唤的【召唤物&middot;紊乱雷球】的传递伤害的伤害来源不正确的问题 。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-AcTydXaGDo9p2HxDyzfcEe1knNb\">✦ 修复了在联机委托中部分情况下队友在退出副本后，队友名称会显示异常的问题。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-QPYIdrEjZoxM5jxSOcJchSs7nng\">✦ 修复了部分文本翻译错误的问题。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-QPYIdrEjZoxM5jxSOcJchSs7nng\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<div data-lark-html-role=\"root\"><span style=\"color: rgb(248, 153, 52);\"><strong><span class=\"text-only\" data-eleid=\"3\">2025年11月12日</span></strong> </span></div>\n<div data-lark-html-role=\"root\"><span class=\"text-only\" data-eleid=\"5\">✦ 修复了部分文本翻译错误的问题。</span></div>\n<div data-lark-html-role=\"root\"><span class=\"text-only\" data-eleid=\"7\">✦ 优化了移动端部分低配机型在冰湖城联机广场区域的流畅度。</span></div>\n<div data-lark-html-role=\"root\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div data-page-id=\"AoBqdRHRcocZuxxkwPPc9llrn9g\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-RWUvdMa02oxC2vxBcPYcmLNNneh\"><span style=\"color: rgb(248, 153, 52);\"><strong>2025年11月11日</strong></span></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-RWUvdMa02oxC2vxBcPYcmLNNneh\">\n<div data-lark-html-role=\"root\"><span class=\"text-only\" data-eleid=\"5\">✦ 修复了沉浸式戏剧部分界面的红点显示异常的问题（若部分狩月人仍有红点显示，可关闭游戏5分钟后重新进入游戏即可消除异常显示的红点）。</span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-KOXTdRZfqoiOKQxdjQPcPcXXnJb\">✦ 修复了沉浸式戏剧中部分超过150级的怪物，生命值有概率出现异常的问题。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-IwQkds1EyoQYesx5ztncOYUan7c\">✦ 修复了据点乐曲《Redemption 救赎》播放的对应曲目不正确的问题。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-IwQkds1EyoQYesx5ztncOYUan7c\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<div data-page-id=\"JIJzdE7oGoWIzVxeirNc5OmOnFb\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-RoVUd9inEo6tadxybvicG1bNnah\"><span style=\"color: rgb(248, 153, 52);\"><strong>2025年11月10日</strong></span></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-NTyfd9XXhoAvCGxb05Gc1JtFnzc\">✦ 修复了印象值系列成就的文本描述错误的问题。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-U4dzdO36noUhvjxowQRcyVdCn5c\">✦ 修复了部分文本翻译错误的问题。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-U4dzdO36noUhvjxowQRcyVdCn5c\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<div data-page-id=\"QCcYd4hiFoBq3ix5XyucE1X5nor\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-O6chdyWJWoU7urxXidmciNpDnTd\"><span style=\"color: rgb(248, 153, 52);\"><strong>2025年11月07日</strong></span></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Dk4FdoCn7ohUNBxLtuocPWdDnFc\">✦ 修复了在梦魇残声结算界面通过查看档案跳转至个人主页会卡死的问题。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-MXzFdJsK1oPxFUxEo6vcS0HvnDe\">✦ 修复了在切换设备后活动系统的红点会显示异常的问题。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-F8EadXXoQomsUExUcurchgZgn1e\">✦ 修复了在投票选择撤退/继续界面，如果点击继续的速度较快，会导致界面卡住的问题。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Rw1zdhtMqop2LDx1i98cxTJAnah\">✦ 修复了文明博弈中常规博弈部分任务无法完成的问题。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Rw1zdhtMqop2LDx1i98cxTJAnah\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-VbfRdNilComhW6xyk3PcfKj3nuW\"><span style=\"color: rgb(248, 153, 52);\"><strong>2025年11月06日</strong></span></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-ATCKdgBdqo6ysBx6zNbczq4hnsf\">\n<div data-page-id=\"CbVlddPoAoU2M9xYgGxcAYMtnuf\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-UmoTdhpDgoKERhxcPIAcwVwNnue\">✦ 修复了部分用户使用外挂等非法手段获取非上线角色的漏洞，目前已对该部分用户进行封禁并扣除非法获取的奖励。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-MXvNdekuwooLGKxCdP2cMjGWnvc\">✦ 修复了松露与榛子在联机委托中使用【饱饱工作】后使用【蹄蹄大冲撞】容易撞停的问题。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-WKIadNiADo7s8Mx59SlcBqQBn0g\">✦ 修复了在委托密函副本刷新临界点进行匹配进入，有概率会导致结算异常的问题。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-LKK9dX9Zfoo9BExjwzbcw5PanQg\">✦ 修复了部分文本翻译错误的问题。</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-ATCKdgBdqo6ysBx6zNbczq4hnsf\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div data-page-id=\"KUWJdPwbZo9PeUxqnRtcyZLNnP2\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-VbfRdNilComhW6xyk3PcfKj3nuW\"><span style=\"color: rgb(248, 153, 52);\"><strong>2025年11月05日</strong></span></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-ATCKdgBdqo6ysBx6zNbczq4hnsf\">✦ 新增了部分用于后续活动的游戏内道具。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-VjHFdh9X7o1574xoBmucUAIKnMb\">✦ 修复了在锻造界面如果点击全部领取，会提示系统报错的问题。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-VjHFdh9X7o1574xoBmucUAIKnMb\">\n<div data-page-id=\"KUWJdPwbZo9PeUxqnRtcyZLNnP2\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-FLbWdaHeeoPidnxnBaWcn88hnZb\">✦ 修复了部分iOS设备邮件文本换行显示异常的问题。</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-G295dhXMjoTdMpx747BckIVfngy\">✦ 修复了部分文本翻译错误的问题。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-OgXNd848Eos91XxrwaLc26gMnEh\">✦ 优化了部分场景下的显存占用。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-VvgZdyfkDocxEpxh6UacPtm9nGc\">✦ 优化了侍者皎皎的「月度订单」的购买奖励与每日奖励。</div>\n<ul class=\"list-bullet1\">\n<li class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-T5DydMw6fobJ3kxvv4ZcoXwTnmh\" data-list=\"bullet\">\n<div>购买奖励额外增加：委托手册&middot;四*1</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-TqQ2dH1qIoeOqJxt3yAcLRFonvc\" data-list=\"bullet\">\n<div>每日签到奖励额外增加：委托手册&middot;二*1</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-EnHmdug7ooVvhbxAgy5cpGNVnLd\" data-list=\"bullet\">\n<div>对于此前已经购买的玩家我们将根据上述调整内容，进行道具补发。</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div data-page-id=\"GPPEdvKWwoViuUxHt0kc8yCVnnb\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnPMF4l602hHIqbJQTEbG2uc\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcn2t1p3RkvVGTpZYw14i9RRb\">《二重螺旋》运营团队</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
                ["language"] = "CN",
                ["title1"] = "更新修复说明",
            },
        },
    },
