                ["body"] = "<p><img src=\"http://pan01-cdn-dna-ali.shyxhy.com/upload/01-限时活动 -【活跃活动】文明博弈活动说明.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"728\" height=\"200\"></p>\n<div data-page-id=\"Hk2OdR3eroIEHxxGtGQc2W69n4b\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Garsd9ZmIolj1nxTprmcBNZFnHe\"><strong>【活动时间】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-FKDhdJybSo2f7OxTeFWchRhTnlb\">2025年11月03日 10:00 ~ 2025年11月25日 04:59（UTC+8）</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-DjqGdwi1loo3LIxDryCccrSOn79\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-MD81d7LC0onoIwxg1wDcsTaanag\"><strong>【开放条件】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-ExlNdIi2eoSCP7xCcNCcwhJznLR\">完成夜航篇第一章剧情【前往少女所说的宅邸】并开启【活动】功能</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-ZW94dABbXo5UPRxEX9YcLYpOnnu\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-DcnKdSaoRoOQFixvvyCcYtJUneh\"><strong>【奖励内容】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Eg3pdVb0qoItrBxDSnbcYHOunkg\">「委托密函线索」、「暮夜的履迹」、「移转模块」、「武器移转模块」、「武器说明书」、「战斗旋律」、「铜币」</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-RMB8dKy7coXbASxfaX4c1tQGnIg\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-MEQIdMwZUo7xnWx02NVcsG4WnFg\"><strong>【活动说明】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-CjdYddvHBoqYeSxIVSmcVUNanCc\">活动分为【常规博弈】与【挑战博弈】。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-SncHdMJiho24ehxfF75cI4IZn1g\">在【常规博弈】中，每天可以完成4个&ldquo;每日博弈&rdquo;任务，与2个可重复完成的&ldquo;重复博弈&rdquo;任务。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Qh22dDANVoegnWxnF70cesy5nPm\">完成博弈任务可以获得「皎皎积分」，次日会根据今日的「皎皎积分」进行结算奖励。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-XsWDdfCj1oInQXx1SbBc3yOanAb\">超过每日皎皎积分上限的部分，将转化为铜币。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-P3pHdfTjXohGm4xjObscs6xsnlb\">在【挑战博弈】中，完成挑战&ldquo;博弈任务&rdquo;，可获得「挑战积分」。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-JD01dWjObojQdXxavqGchqe6nQg\">随着时间的流逝，打打打打打劫皎皎会想出来新的【博弈任务】。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-V0mgde2rroJBeOxXEI0cTrrJnPf\">累计达到10、20、30、40、50「挑战积分」可以领取阶段奖励。</div>\n</div>",
