        ["Content"] = {
            [1] = {
                ["title"] = "版本内容总览",
                ["body"] = "<div data-page-id=\"Xq9JdjHCGowTjnxCKzBcmflon7e\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<div data-page-id=\"Xq9JdjHCGowTjnxCKzBcmflon7e\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<div data-page-id=\"Xq9JdjHCGowTjnxCKzBcmflon7e\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<h3 class=\"heading-3 ace-line old-record-id-KgzjduInLopkCOxnP4QcjX3qnCb\"><strong>★开放区域一览★</strong></h3>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-NpNXdvwtMoxskXxOqLac24M4n1b\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-WsvSdYkLzocJx2xoglSc88jSnGb\">✦ <strong>净界岛地区开放</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-NcZpdHKznoEti1xSbXJcXmOwnNh\">一座与世隔绝的孤岛，村民们在此过着平静的生活，直到意外来临的那一天。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Ha4QdPEXKoNLzWxU7RkcetTgnlg\"><strong>✦</strong> <strong>科赛托斯行省部分地区开放</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-CP6gd5n4WolUrex44Jucl1ysn2c\"><strong>「冰湖城」</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-AhmYd4IquouZpHxsuETcBRf0n0c\">海伯利亚扼守北方边境的要塞城市，亦是帝国最早的城市之一。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-O6o6de6xvo5bqnx3sskcW9SsnYc\">因城郊长年封冻的湖泊&ldquo;泪湖&rdquo;而得名。这里气候严寒，每年只有为期约三个月的&ldquo;融雪季&rdquo;。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Ig6ddEAvpov6H6xDi1Kc46A6ndg\"><strong>「冰湖城 &middot; 盖雷亚剧院」 </strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-QnwrdV8ZyoepLuxOvhWcNSD7nSe\">盖雷亚剧院，建立于冰湖城最繁荣的年代，无数名伶在这里献上精湛表演，成为黄金岁月最耀眼的点缀。然而，随着月石矿脉的枯竭，浮华褪去，剧院也逐渐冷清。只有那些稍显过时的经典剧目，以及带着怀旧气息的轻喜剧，还在诉说着这座城市独特的文化脉搏。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-RSHudstpkoJHPfxbMFpcJ0LmnGb\"><strong>「冰湖城 &middot; 下水道」 </strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-M7qodU1s4oAvKaxfhmxc6dK4n0c\">由海伯利亚人修建的，横亘冰湖城内外的巨大地下排水网络。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-DOGudZjLJo8XASxTiXAcwe5GnRf\">随着月髓科技的发展，大量工业废水被排进下水道，为了解决垃圾堵塞和水体冻结的问题，帝国在下水道安装了大量装置，用于垃圾粉碎、防冻、阻断或引导水流等。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-JzpOdsL5LoAAv2xN1XRcHD4gnrh\"><strong>「格雷姆废矿」</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-KjxkdtOE8o1YHPxVHyLcgSoinnb\">曾是海伯利亚最大的月石矿场之一，在矿脉衰竭后逐渐被废弃。虽然已经沦为秽兽的巢穴，但传说中里面仍留有一些宝贵的矿物。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-LpPbdGrEConH7IxfbJjcAqGRnFc\"><strong>「龙莎要塞」</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-STJMdNcy7o74iWx7gokcY67Dnpg\">海伯利亚帝国的知名要塞之一，位于玛瑙河谷边的高地，一度是扼守皇都与红溪城来往水路的交通要道。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-GJvNdGVmco021oxW7FBcLjXwnac\">帝国根基尚未稳固时，初代皇帝盖雷亚曾在此设伏，顺利击败敌对联军，这场胜利成为了海伯利亚建立的基石。经过历代工程师的不懈建设，要塞内部分布着诸多复杂的防御机关。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-HE1vdea52othmbxBoBrcsbptnod\">然而，该要塞已被神弃者同盟占领长达数月，至今未能收复。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-BGYXdvTnfoZM2cxEasjcKHMTnXd\">&nbsp;</div>\n<h3 class=\"heading-3 ace-line old-record-id-Si4hdJQb7ojvGdxf8ELcaGWVn59\"><strong>★主线章节开放★</strong></h3>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-KUp0d3PD4oHRlDxy1Fnc8Cl0noh\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-HISEdf7uWoog4JxXRAJcXwfdnJc\"><strong>✦ 夜航篇 序章 涉过沙海的你</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Dt64dxnTqoJ2oAxFwBtcnjIsnbg\">不断重复的梦境，无法看清的梦中人，遥远的呼唤&hellip;&hellip;这一切究竟是幻想还是预言？ 已经没有踌躇的闲暇，平静的生活已被秽兽撕碎。必须活下去，哪怕&mdash;&mdash;逃离故乡。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-N8oEdYhENoHYxzxOtJocffDnn8n\"><strong>✦ 夜航篇 第一章 黑铁&middot;白花 </strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-TsVSdQGc9o7qg8xhmcOcRPagnlg\">陌生的帝国，冰冷的雪原，未知的城市，翩然而至的少女，谜团重重的旅店&hellip;&hellip;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-TYDadtzBKoi7lCxbGZ9ckZemnzb\">背负着过去与使命，成为&ldquo;狩月人&rdquo;完成委托，并一步一步走近&ldquo;恶魔之子&rdquo;的秘密吧。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-GnvsdcRZ1oy0Jpx3rWacLoCTnvg\"><strong>✦ 夜航篇 第二章 雪国的孩子</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Xp1Cd5EGkoAwSnx8n5hcqEK6nDf\">自袭击中奇迹生还，紧握细不可查的蛛丝马迹，与卫戍部队准尉同走缉凶之路。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-IHCHdYbrdoNsAWx2nA8c4xHknCd\">旧日的歌声成为今日的伏笔，前进吧，揭开幕布后的真相，当你就位，好戏开场。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-HHe5dbCf2oDWiLxogjRcnI2unBb\"><strong>✦ 泊暮篇 第一章 俯瞰者的游戏</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-PRuTdFuggoX1GuxHRcNcN5qFnte\">置身于帝国与神弃者同盟争夺要塞的战场，作为帝国的年轻军官，你的战斗刚刚开始。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-U6mBdFxhpoiJLUxRS2zcS6sCnMH\">然而即使面对炮火也从不退缩的你，即将窥见海伯利亚的暗面&mdash;&mdash;那些比子弹和炮火更可怖的东西。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Wd29dfcgVoXrgax4f8lcPkO5nlh\">&nbsp;</div>\n<h3 class=\"heading-3 ace-line old-record-id-YjMNdZme7o6wIaxMIovc24XGnoh\"><strong>★登场角色一览★</strong></h3>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-QLsMd5nEmo3q0yxKFhDcXTmDnjb\">「狩月人」、「妮弗尔夫人」、「莉兹贝尔」、「菲娜」、「赛琪」、「松露与榛子」、「丽蓓卡」、「琳恩」、「西比尔」、「塔比瑟」、「幻景」、「玛尔洁」、「海尔法」、「耶尔与奥利弗」、「奥特赛德」、「达芙涅」、「黎瑟」、「兰迪」、「贝蕾妮卡」</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-YeHxdg26EoAsnOxk9QAc8xS2nTO\">&nbsp;</div>\n<h3 class=\"heading-3 ace-line old-record-id-BfdkdJjXJofd0Hx6MizcRjeHnKh\"><strong>★武器一览★</strong></h3>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-FVfcdY3rYoonIIx5JebcPtVHnBh\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-VSJbdPVbGoK0I4xqfyCcgnpUnn2\"><strong>✦ 远程武器</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-W8Lmdhj8yoVeTlxnYNlc1qv9nfc\">弓「弧光百劫」「茵布拉花序」「裂魂」「烈焰孤沙」</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Athrdsc3boLha8xBb7ncPtbbnOp\">榴炮「群星无意赦免」「崩解」「归墟棘轮」「银白敕令」</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-U9ycd6zyIo9SjtxKVr7c4baxnoe\">双枪「蓝色脉动」「赘生」「告谕圣音」</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-JDl7dXgJPoWTlMxdQ3scwDMKnGh\">手枪「无序奇点」「剥离」「告谕圣言」</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-L3QJdeXD1o8nqXx59r9c59JDn1f\">突击枪「引浪小调」「破晓赞美诗」「织梦的白羽」「放逐怒雷」「销骨」「祈请净火」</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Ogw9d0QJvoXwTVxa1STcnHTRnie\">霰弹枪「缄默育种者」「爆破艺术」「嘶鸣」「圣裁日」</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-ByjzdJjKUohEw1xajIAckE2Knpg\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-LmpUdb3ERoOvT1xDZurcMiLrn3o\"><strong>✦ 近战武器</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-PN8RdY1g1o4egDxnkzTcMQP8nwc\">重剑「惩戒的炼火」「铸铁者」「焦渴」</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-EUBqdY1FNoCsiBxG2vicTnJhnr1\">双刀「失乡的獠牙」「鎏金岁月」「幽鲨眼」</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-DHSOdhg7boImjYxrnA4cYzz6nSY\">太刀「红叶一滴」「凋零」「蒙恩御礼」</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-R2YndQjjdoUw57xxWbEcSZkznIh\">长柄武器「希冀的丰稔」「塞壬的拥吻」「春块戟」「枯朽」</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-LgIed95xToNPJlxb74zcN6m9nte\">单手剑「慧谋的攻守」「孤子的缚锁」「辉珀刃」「追忆的残影」「流浪的蔷薇」</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-CbOvdmlwdo09BTxb3gTcuydMnfc\">剑鞭「不渝的梦海」「缠结」「苍瑚凝碧」</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Q36pdHbXWopxf1xNLHbcw8R8nae\">&nbsp;</div>\n<h3 class=\"heading-3 ace-line old-record-id-YQoMdn6kXoD279xgMwlcaodbnvc\"><strong>✦特色系统展示✦</strong></h3>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-D5BCdSjx5o53tux8cdEc2RhknDg\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Fj2IdrWOXorRluxaUWtcFqxQnhh\"><strong>✦魔之楔</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-O6AKdh6jboLcEvxHbLncyBEXnMe\">开启尘封的魔之匣，破译战斗的古老密语；如影随形，是冒险路上锤炼能力的关键秘宝，亦是攀登强者之壁的进化宝典。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-YRB1dSOntoqO1dxQ6o5cCkQKnGb\">&bull; 完成「委托」收集各类魔之楔，装备后能显著强化角色与武器的战斗能力。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Yn2Ydx20SouoqJxNDNTccyHcnRf\">&bull; 特别设有「魔之匣」：专属任务助你快速掌握技巧；提供完整图鉴与配置推荐，帮你轻松找到最适合你的魔之楔搭配方案。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Vx0gdm1ZToqUoOxqHk9cwSmvnVf\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-JLBUd2diyoT9GrxJxFZchTe7nHd\"><strong>✦ 魔灵捕捉与培育</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-ROYddbAZLozfBexjCIDcfEcpn4g\">在广袤的阿特拉西亚大陆，生活着一群独特的生物，它们介于动物与秽兽之间，虽有着秽兽般的魔法能力，但却只需要一点&ldquo;妙罐罐&rdquo;，就可以成为人们的好伙伴。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-VbJgd4GoCoqg9jxDlTXcbncBnw6\">&bull; 开放捕捉的部分魔灵：</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-JEq4d2Hw3oazWAxA557cfxksnWc\">五星魔灵「好梦先生」、「珍珠兔」、「你好箱」</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Ej8rdlv2OoGnw2xs7ZtcEAvJnef\">四星魔灵「球球蜂」、「浮鱿灯」、「糖霜白兔」、「摇摇火尾」、「噼啪猫车」、「绵绵草」、「摇摇冻」</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-DpyAdTG9foYVZ1x7UeOctLIbnFh\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-N3aldsHlJocuEkx63IccCRjmnOf\"><strong>✦ 收集铸造</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-BMRZd4c5PolwknxoWL7cdSsOnPf\">无论是精工细造，还是战场应急，「铸造」都能使冒险之旅事半功倍。铁匠皎皎已将必备物品清单理好，让前辈的智慧助你一臂之力。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-PV4kdkDDgobhurxkT0JcZbnnnIM\">&bull; 冒险和探索途中可获得设计图纸和铸造材料，解锁铁匠皎皎支线任务，即可随时随地体验铸造功能。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Qkbadp3nnoymYuxyBTPc9r2bnXi\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-UUuLdCef9ok0w9xZCTJc6ZGYn4w\"><strong>✦ 联机共斗</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-K34cdceIcoKmpHxfA53cEbBXnwg\">生命是航行在无尽长夜里的孤船，河流泪水满溢，夹岸荆棘丛生。当你我的航道交错，不妨用手中的浆板助彼此一臂之力，让这趟旅行得以走得更远&hellip;&hellip;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-XRrhdBMlaoDhGNxKiZEcsE62nHg\">&bull; 在冒险和探索途中，狩月人可以在特定区域遇见彼此，招呼问候；亦或结伴组队，一同完成各项委托。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Q92KdQA2FoH4PexmZMPcSiydnhf\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-VCa8d8fmgorx2SxCrcocX1MAnOc\"><strong>✦ 形象</strong><strong>衣饰</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-KhJGdLXs3oKbvgxkfBYcGGiKnWf\">「梦中的舞会」「阳光磨坊」「父辈余荫」&hellip;&hellip;全新角色形象与武器形象华美登场，随心搭配，尽显独特风采！更有精致趣味衣饰、个性武器挂饰、各式角色动作静待探索，开启属于你的风格之旅。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-IHOcdHy1RobsYsxXpmrcMlm5nCB\">&bull; 相关形象获取资讯，可在游戏中打开「整备」，进入衣饰界面查看。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-U93NdqZYNoYHOtxRkSmc0Op8n2L\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-P679dbv9VobNcfxqcl4cJGJdnmg\"><strong>✦</strong><strong> 形象</strong><strong>与染色</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Al1VdgAH7oVoeqxcLEIcTXjmnVe\">泪湖、海盐、林梢......将世间万物的色彩赋予你的装扮吧！</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-SGTcdzFBnofKILxwj3EcWfd7nwd\">&bull; 打开「整备」，选择武器或角色形象进入染色界面，即可体验全新的染色功能，打造独一无二的个性造型。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-WpFsdmilzopQUoxgU1icyRKpnOc\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-QiFTdKGOqoZ4dYxxbgecmoWRnZe\"><strong>✦ 其他系统</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Z9Xcdcyp7oJn74xhZ28cVqmvnTe\">&bull; 角色点滴：收集「欢乐」、「悲伤」、「愤怒」等思绪，解锁各式光阴集，即可体验不同角色的专属剧情，了解其背后的故事。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-EUKfdaGCxomMV4xysTgceTyOnQd\">&bull; 图鉴百科：解读世界观与剧情设定，兼收角色/怪物/物品资料，助您全方位理解阿特拉西亚大陆文化。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-O8wJdIuSQopHmJxz2u4cRhWgnad\">&bull; 场景音律：休憩之所音乐自由切换，营造个性化氛围。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-LCuId9Mn5oWoI2xtbbIctd1Inzg\">&bull; 休闲垂钓：特定水域开放休闲垂钓玩法，享受片刻宁静。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-GbevdVgrFoOcOrx073Jch8vXnIh\">&bull; 伙伴派遣：指派同伴处理各地突发的特殊事件，获取丰厚回报。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Z3T9dPYLOoetlUxmjubcY2bInQd\">&bull; 个性展示：全新个人主页、特色头像框及头像系统，展现独特风采。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-V6BMdHFkKoV1E3xQYazczDlPnmg\">&nbsp;</div>\n<h3 class=\"heading-3 ace-line old-record-id-IOIrdyANmoOHngxRucqcR3Z4ndc\"><strong>★玩法挑战开启★</strong></h3>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-P1Bwdm1ECoZEUYxTVBVc420Vn5Y\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-RQCRdailKoukRyxEpgBc7CtHnad\">✦ <strong>皎皎的「委托」发布</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-E570dA9EboeQ3mxlEiHcHhU5nRg\">【常规委托】勘察地形、探险毒雾地带、驱逐秽兽、扼守绮晶、追缉敌首......接受来自皎皎的委托，获取丰厚报酬使用「委托手册」，可提升「常规委托」的委托报酬。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-CH7vdLHthoQfL6xKnqpcXAJBnhc\">【魔之楔系列委托】「夜航手册」持续开放中&mdash;&mdash; 完成委托即可获得丰厚报酬，使用「委托手册」，可提升「夜航手册」的委托报酬。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-FtsedqYXYokP1bx87YiciFhFnRb\">【委托密函】开启角色、武器、魔之楔密函，全角色&amp;全武器免费刷，爽斗火力无上限，来打造你的顶级阵容吧！</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-JkSgdOLQooxPWkxZ5JRc1oiJnYf\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-UqF5dezIkoHVDyx63gMczxaCnGb\">✦<strong>「梦魇残声」每周挑战开启</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-CwDIdlz1SoPkymxt3ZZclOpLngb\">海伯利亚帝国第十三军团军团长、格雷姆废矿深处的巨大秽兽......过往的记忆碎片，纷纷化作梦魇，卷土重来。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-AsQxdHJF2o5nu1xS3EIcEaHJnTg\">开放条件: 完成夜航篇第一章剧情「乘着轻柔的风」</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-X3XndeBAyoUJ5SxGjyIcPZJ3nZb\">奖励内容: 技能升级材料、角色/武器委托密函等。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-InZ2dNe5eoov8Lx89G1cmtsTnad\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-RtN7dBTvLoulA3x0aVMcdbXAnsk\">✦ <strong>迷津卷一「乐土之国的深渊」现已开放</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-WKbZdHah2oPvOYx4Yp9c1EKinoc\">探索深渊，应对各种类型的随机挑战，在与深渊幽影的较量中，不断成长变强。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-T0xwdVwYGoL0zQxUnLhcf5pRnee\">开放条件: 完成夜航篇第一章剧情「乘着轻柔的风」</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-JSxkdNNhFoJjxpxjkE1c3oGbnmd\">奖励内容: 密函：莉兹贝尔、思绪片段&middot;莉兹贝尔、时之纺线、魔之楔、角色/魔之楔养成素材、铜币等</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Nc4odnviDo8Ph1xF2rmc4Y5GnYb\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-UGaZd5GAdoYPJFxmyuqcdLQbnVE\">✦ <strong>「沉浸式戏剧」演出剧目正在上映</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-OucadAYVwoxu0IxvH3qcMwnCnmL\">剧中人，欢迎你的到来，这一次你不再袖手旁观，而是一往无前的主演，战胜敌人，向所有人证明主角的资质，获得充斥喜悦的完美结局吧！</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Th0ydp5ieo0LBxx20incBG1Cn87\">开放条件: 完成泊暮篇剧情「审判日」</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-GEWQdn7ERoYuiNxAKq6ceWEmnJc\">奖励内容：角色密函、武器密函、委托密函线索、角色/武器/魔之楔/魔灵养成材料、魔之楔、铜币等。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-AVeDdaWC7oOWR2xvePgcRmuznBe\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-XpHidrkWcoJgNYx3NLgcYpLNnfh\">✦ <strong>阿特拉西亚大陆探索指南</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Fyqud4BiVoQVwoxsTnjcHK0anCb\">这片神秘大陆蕴藏着无数待解的奇遇：</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-ZISVdyJ65oKOBHxcgQgc6Bk4nnb\">&bull; <strong>探险之证收集</strong>：跟随传奇探险家皎皎留下的足迹，找寻散落各地的探险之证，兑换专属奖励。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-KGIDdAhyIoo8pAxPzUkcmG5KnWb\">&bull; <strong>羊角魔灵寻踪</strong>：邂逅神秘的羊角羊蹄人身魔灵，它们神出鬼没，一旦找到踪迹便能收获惊喜。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-LifYd4GxnoNLmexWWtoctfZUnVd\">&bull; <strong>遗落的纸张</strong>：无论是卷轴，羊皮纸，还是印刷品，它们都有一个共同点&mdash;&mdash;指向着&ldquo;宝藏&rdquo;的所在地。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-BijKdf8dLo3NhGx60cmc9Nmgn1c\">&bull; <strong>宝箱探索</strong>：发掘散落各地的惊喜宝箱，每件秘匣都暗藏独特的开启玄机。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-BtkldiIqpoTFNMxG0OKcz4XinOK\">奖励内容: 历练经验、委托密函线索、锻造素材、铜币等。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-ArjddHQJ1oJ0hFxorrAcXIhBnGf\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-CaTXd7IDeoC76OxccBzcmmYEnc0\"><strong>✦ 「灵鸟试炼」挑战开启</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-DI0adXeKRoKD8kxbPxkczhSrnvg\">激活传送点「梦中的灵鸟」，于此静心冥想，即可踏入灵鸟的试炼之境，通过层层试炼，证明你也有翱翔天际的资格吧。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-RjCxdrfkeo3d8wxgdP4cuxqNnBe\">开放条件：完成夜航篇第一章剧情「猎物与猎人」并激活任意传送点，可解锁对应挑战</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-V8H9dxKiyoRATnxPjJNcx3aZntd\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-GHhsdlc1XoJD9sxJEtpczW8tnRc\">《二重螺旋》运营团队</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-GAKvdExWioLqy3xcyxDcnY27nW3\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
